Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: ttyconv
Version: 1.0
Summary: Convert a TTY from one encoding to another
Home-page: http://www.bedroomlan.org/projects/ttyconv
Author: Alexios Chouchoulas
Author-email: alexios@bedroomlan.org
License: GNU GPL v2
Description: Translates a TTY connection from one character encoding to
        another. This is useful when, for instance, you have a UTF-8 based
        desktop with national language and keyboard support and you still want
        to connect to systems that are unaware of this, or use a different or
        unusual encoding.
Platform: any
Classifier: Development Status :: 5 - Mature
Classifier: Environment :: Console
Classifier: License :: OSI Approved :: GNU General Public License (GPL)
Classifier: Natural Language :: English
Classifier: Operating System :: OS Independent
Classifier: Programming Language :: Python :: 2.4
Classifier: Programming Language :: Python :: 2.5
Classifier: Programming Language :: Python :: 2.6
Classifier: Topic :: Utilities
